<div style='background-color: #faf2f2; padding: 20px;'>
  <div style='max-width: 300px; margin: 0 auto;'>
    <a href="https://www.theholisticpanda.com" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="https://<%= ENV['CDN_URL'] %>/logo.png" alt="TheHolisticPanda" style="width: 300px;"></a>
  </div>
  <h3>Dear <%= @practitioner.user.first_name %>,</h3>

  <% if @session.free_session %>
    <p>Don't forget to click 'Completed' on your completed session. This applies to sessions with no charges, such as a free assessment/session or an influencer collaboration with The Holistic Panda.</p>
  <% else %>
    <p>We noticed you didn’t charge your session <%= @session.service.name %> with <%= @session.user.full_name %>. You’ll need to do so to receive your payout.</p>
  <% end %>

  <% if @session.free_session %>
    <h4>Here is a simple user guide on how to do this:</h4>
  <% else %>
    <h4>Here is a simple user guide on how to charge your session:</h4>
  <% end %>
  <ul>
    <li><p>Click button below or click "sessions as practitioner" under the drop-down menu after logging into your account.</p></li>
    <li><p>Go to the "Pending payment" tab.</p></li>
    <% if @session.free_session %>
      <li><p>Find the completed session and click "Completed".</p></li>
    <% else %>
      <li><p>Find the completed session and click "Charge".</p></li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <br>
  <%= link_to 'Charge your session', practitioner_sessions_url, target: "_blank", style: 'text-decoration: none; background-color: #e57850!important; color: white; padding: 8px 24px; border-radius: 3px;' %>
  <br>
  <p>If you have any questions or need support, please contact us at <a href="mailto:practitioner@theholisticpanda.com" style="text-decoration: none; color: #366735;">practitioner@theholisticpanda.com</a>. We're here to help!</p>
  <br>
  <p>Yours,</p>
  <p>The Holistic Panda Team</p>
